Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.87,0:05:40.08,Kaguya,,0,0,0,,A pak se naše srdce stanou jedním.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.62,0:05:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(972,577)}"FESTIVAL HOUSHIN"
